legacy.description: 🇨🇳 Chinese Ambassador to the State of Qatar
legacy.name: Zhou Jian

legacy.full_text: Dear Qatari friends, I will soon fly back to China with Qatar Airways and end my tenure. A close friend afar brings a distant land near. I wish to say thank you to all friends for your support & help these years. My best wishes to Qatar and China-Qatar friendship. Goodbye, Qatar! https://t.co/lXVgiqKktb

legacy.description: 🇨🇳 Chinese Ambassador to the State of Qatar
legacy.name: Zhou Jian

legacy.full_text: Held yesterday a farewell reception with Chinese nationals in Qatar. My past three and a half years as the Chinese Ambassador to Qatar has been fruitful and full of memories, and I wish to thank all our compatriots who supported me and contributed to China-Qatar relations.🇨🇳🇶🇦 https://t.co/MB8CXpagzs

legacy.description: 🇨🇳 Chinese Ambassador to the State of Qatar
legacy.name: Zhou Jian

legacy.full_text: I was also presented a special farewell gift from a Qatari student learning Chinese, which is a painting of my audience with HH the Amir. I would like to thank him and all young Qatari friends he was representing. Hope our bilateral friendship will be evergreen in the future!

legacy.name: Zhou Jian

legacy.full_text:
Serving for 3 years & a half, I am proud to contribute my part to China-Qatar strategic partnership. I wish to thank all Qatari brothers who care and support our bilateral ties, and hope our cooperation will be more successful in the future.
My heart will always be with Qatar!
